# AI SDR Assistant

An AI-powered Sales Development Representative (SDR) assistant built with Python, Streamlit, and the OpenAI API.

## Features

- 🔍 Prospect and company research
- ✉️ Personalized cold email generation
- 💼 LinkedIn outreach message generation
- 📞 Sales call opener generation
- 📧 Follow-up email sequences
- 📊 Lead qualification scoring
- 📝 CRM-ready prospect summaries

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- OpenAI API
- Git
- GitHub

## Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
```

